        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "A rare disorder characterized by slowly progressive spasticity extrapyramidal movement disorders (dystonia choreoathetosis and rigidity) cerebellar ataxia moderate to severe cognitive deficit and anarthria/dysarthria. Patients present with distinctive MRI findings of diffuse hypomyelination of the cerebral hemispheres mild to severe cerebellar atrophy and atrophy of the basal nuclei."
        },
